&lt;p&gt;Our Growth Marketing Specialist will thrive in the weeds: launching campaigns, pulling keyword reports, adjusting bids, standing up A/B tests, and constantly looking for the next channel or angle to test. You&#39;ll work across Google, Meta, YouTube, Apple Search Ads, and emerging channels - we are constantly expanding. If you love the combination of analytical rigor and creative experimentation that defines great growth marketing, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is based in Los Angeles or San Francisco.&lt;/p&gt;
