&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paid campaign execution &amp;amp; reporting&lt;/strong&gt;: Launch, manage, and optimize campaigns across Google Ads (Search, PMax), Meta/Instagram, YouTube, TikTok, and emerging channels (Reddit, ChatGPT, Apple Search Ads). Monitor performance daily and keep reporting on spend, CAC, and efficiency metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
