&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Agency &amp;amp; vendor management&lt;/strong&gt;: Own day-to-day relationships with external agencies and vendors across podcast, creative, UGC, and affiliate channels — managing deliverables, timelines, and performance accountability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creative performance analysis&lt;/strong&gt;: Partner with in-house creative and agency teams to analyze what&#39;s working across ad creative, identify top performers, and feed data-driven insights back into future creative iterations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
