&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 years of hands-on experience in growth marketing, performance marketing, or paid acquisition — internships and agency experience count&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Google Ads and Meta Ads Manager; bonus if you&#39;ve also worked in TikTok, YouTube, or other platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable pulling keyword reports, adjusting bids

