&lt;p&gt;This opportunity here is to define how revenue operations scale inside a high-growth AI company. This is a hands-on, systems-oriented role suited for someone who has built GTM Engineering foundations at a growing SaaS company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting directly to the Head of Sales, you’ll have wide scope and visibility.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Own&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
