&lt;li&gt;Strong proficiency in Python (for ETL/scripting) and SQL (for data modeling).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with cloud platforms (AWS/GCP) and data technologies like Kafka, Spark, and Snowflake/Databricks.&lt;/li&gt;
